622
00:38:55,090 --> 00:38:59,010
So there's a square root of
some square, some quadratic.

623
00:38:59,010 --> 00:39:02,010
It's very much
like this business.

624
00:39:02,010 --> 00:39:04,830
But it isn't of
any of these forms.

625
00:39:04,830 --> 00:39:06,360
And so what I want
to do is show you

626
00:39:06,360 --> 00:39:10,540
