640
00:40:03,640 --> 00:40:08,220
The only choice in order to
get something like x^2 + 4x out

641
00:40:08,220 --> 00:40:11,440
of this, is to take a to be 2.

642
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:16,950
Because then, this
